  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，描述一个多阶段处理流程。整体上有三个主要阶段：First、Second和Third。从初始状态会先进入First。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "First",
        "Second",
        "Third"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，First是核心阶段。那First内部是不是还有子状态？我注意到您强调了这个阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "First"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，First是个复合状态，里面包含1st和2nd两个子状态。而且1st之后还有一个嵌套的innerFirst区域，里面再细分'1 in innerFirst'和'2 in innerFirst'两个状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "First",
        "1st",
        "2nd",
        "innerFirst",
        "1st1st",
        "1st2nd"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把外层结构搭好。First作为复合状态，内部从初始状态进入1st，然后1st连接到innerFirst，innerFirst再连到2nd。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "1st",
        "innerFirst",
        "2nd"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "innerFirst的结构没错，但注意1st1st和1st2nd之间的流向——1st1st要指向1st2nd。另外First本身还要分出两条线分别连到Second和Third。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "1st1st",
        "1st2nd",
        "First",
        "Second",
        "Third"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加First到Second、First到Third的转移。innerFirst内部也从初始状态进入1st1st，再到1st2nd。这样First内部的流转就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "First",
        "Second",
        "Third",
        "1st1st",
        "1st2nd"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Second和Third的终态处理不一样。Second是从2nd直接结束；Third则是从初始状态进入3rd，然后3rd再结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Second",
        "2nd",
        "Third",
        "3rd"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，Second里面2nd指向终态；Third内部从[*]到3rd，再3rd到[*]。我检查一下——First的显示名是不是要改成\"the first composite\"？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Second",
        "Third",
        "First"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，First的显示标签用\"the first composite\"，innerFirst里的1st1st显示为\"1 in innerFirst\"，1st2nd显示为\"2 in innerFirst\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "First",
        "1st1st",
        "1st2nd"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才发现一个问题——我之前想给1st2nd加一条回到1st的线，但这会形成循环。这条线是不是应该去掉？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "1st2nd",
        "1st"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，那条线不要。innerFirst的流转只在内部完成，1st2nd不需要返回1st。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "1st2nd",
        "1st"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已移除那条线。现在整个图结构清晰了：外层三个主状态，First作为复合状态包含嵌套层级，Second和Third各自有明确的终态处理。还有需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "First",
        "Second",
        "Third",
        "innerFirst"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
